    <name>Hash It</name>
    <summary>Generate and verify file hashes</summary>
    <description>
        <p>A tool that allows you to ensure the integrity of files.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Verify files with a reference hash to ensure the integrity of files</li>
            <li>Generate file hashes to allow others to verify your files</li>
            <li>Supports SHA256, SHA1 and MD5 algorithms</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
    <categories>
        <category>Utility</category>
    </categories>
    <custom>
